INSERT INTO `movies` VALUES ('146', '宁浩', '8.5', '疯狂的石头', '郭涛,刘桦,连晋,黄渤,徐峥', 'https://img2.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p712241453.jpg', '2006', '喜剧,犯罪', '中国大陆,中国香港', '汉语普通话,重庆话', '2006-06-30', '106', '721915', '41.9%,44.3%,12.6%,1.0%,0.2%', '重庆一间工艺品厂已经濒临倒闭，却不料在拆倒旧厂房的时候，发现了厕所里的一件宝物——一块价值连城的翡翠。厂里决定用这块翡翠举办一个展览，赚些钱发拖欠了几个月的工人工资。期间由工艺品厂保卫科长包世宏（郭涛 饰）负责看守这件宝物。但是，国际大盗麦克与本地一帮小偷却让包世宏一筹莫展，他们各施其技接近翡翠，展览馆开始了一场明争暗斗的较量。黑色幽默也开始幕幕上演。翡翠的价值几何？最后谁是胜出者？事情远没有表面那么简单……', '[{\"user\": \"\\u5c0f\\u8033\\u6735\\u56fe\\u5417\", \"start\": \"30\", \"time\": \"2006-08-03 02:24:29\", \"content\": \"\\u50cf\\u662f\\u4e2d\\u56fd\\u7248\\u7684\\u4e24\\u6746\\u5927\\u70df\\u67aa\\u3002\"}, {\"user\": \"Doublebitch\", \"start\": \"50\", \"time\": \"2008-11-24 22:20:22\", \"content\": \"\\u4ece\\u8fd9\\u90e8\\u5f00\\u59cb\\u7231\\u4e0a\\u9ec4\\u6e24\"}, {\"user\": \"elvita\", \"start\": \"50\", \"time\": \"2006-07-14 10:26:20\", \"content\": \"\\u771f\\u597d\\u73a9\"}, {\"user\": \"\\u671d\\u66ae\\u96ea\", \"start\": \"50\", \"time\": \"2013-11-19 00:21:35\", \"content\": \"\\u867d\\u7136\\u6709\\u300a\\u4e24\\u6746\\u5927\\u70df\\u67aa\\u300b\\u7684\\u5f71\\u5b50\\uff0c\\u4f46\\u4ecd\\u7136\\u662f\\u4e2d\\u56fd\\u6700\\u4f18\\u79c0\\u7684\\u591a\\u7ebf\\u53d9\\u4e8b\\u7535\\u5f71\\u4e4b\\u4e00\\u3002\"}, {\"user\": \"\\u5e55\\u5929\\u5e2d\\u5730\", \"start\": \"50\", \"time\": \"2017-03-07 08:05:37\", \"content\": \"\\u7b97\\u6bd4\\u8f83\\u7ecf\\u5178\\u7684\\u9ed1\\u8272\\u559c\\u5267\\u7247\\u4e86\\uff0c\\u5f71\\u5e1d\\u771f\\u4e0d\\u662f\\u76d6\\u7684\"}]', 'https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/sqxs/public/p1247531838.jpg,https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/sqxs/public/p2552294328.jpg', 'https://vt1.doubanio.com/202202251716/4c76b4c273bae4d7f712632c8984ea7f/view/movie/M/301430881.mp4', 'https://movie.douban.com/subject/1862151/');
